comment: Crowder (BOS) makes body to body contact with Johnson (MIA) that affects his SQBR.
Horford (BOS) sets the screen on Johnson (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Johnson (MIA) makes contact with Horford's (BOS) arms that affects his driving shot attempt.
Whiteside (MIA) sets the screen on Rozier (BOS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Smart (BOS) legally contests Richardson's (MIA) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Smart (BOS) cleanly strips the ball from Winslow (MIA).
Winslow (MIA) cleanly strips the ball from Horford (BOS).
Smart (BOS) makes contact with Winslow's (MIA) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, Winslow (MIA) is assessed a technical foul and Smart (BOS) is assessed a common foul for the contact on the shot attempt.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Winslow (MIA) commits a take foul on Smart (BOS).
Horford (BOS) legally contests Richardson's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Winslow (MIA) commits a take foul on Rozier (BOS).
